original_title: Trampled By Turtles: Live at First Avenue
overview: Captured over 3 sold out nights in their home town at Minneapolis, First Avenue, this DVD features songs from all 6 Trampled by Turtles' albums, including "Codeine," "Wait So Long" and TBT's version of the Pixies(TM) classic, "Where is My Mind?"
title: Trampled By Turtles: Live at First Avenue
